tva:BasicDescription.tva:Title: TYPICAL MALAYSIAN DRIVERS
tva:BasicDescription.tva:Synopsis: For most Malaysians, we spend most of our time on the road. Get- ting to and from work, or school, Getting stuck in traffic. Getting lost. Looking for a parking spot. Going out to makan. The list goes on. We spend so much time on the road, that we even have a certain character or personality when we are driving.
